  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to test the efficiency of intravenous administration of metoprolol
      versus intravenous administration of amiodarone in the prevention of atrial fibrillation
      after cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
